		<title>16EMPLOYMENT</title>
		<content> There are three main sources of       
 employment in this area-farming,      
 services,and local industries.        
{FARMING-}Has become increasingly      
 mechanised and is not a major employer
 any more.Some farmers have set up     
 their own milk bottling plants instead
 of using the major creameries.        
{SERVICES-}Castlederg is a service town
 for the area and the job situation    
 reflects this.                        
{LOCAL INDUSTRIES-}There are two       
 factories in this area ,Aranderg      
 Furniture and a woollen factory.      
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
